  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you would get a nice gift.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And everybody would wish you a lot of happiness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we are-- but we are Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we always believed in God, and still believe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we have-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we have to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wish I could think of the word-- accept-- OK.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to accept that this was His will.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] Now that it's your birthday, and it's almost simultaneously with mine-- because hers was, like, two weeks later-- I plead with God that he should give us this gift together, [PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] that He should watch our our parents-- our dear parents and our sisters.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And as suddenly as we were-- as suddenly as it happened that we were separated, that He will bring us back together again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I know it's a little difficult now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But don't lose faith.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It's a little cloudy, but it will clear up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] No-- it's a little cloudy now, but next birthday will be that much clearer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There will come a day when the sun will shine for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] and the gate of the camps will open for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we, in our joy, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] will yell, we are free.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And because you had to suffer when you were so young, God will like you that much more, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that you will never face adversity, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] and that you will be happy till you're 120.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
